    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and all electronics functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained example that shows zero signs of wear.",
